statements: SELECT * FROM vehicle_sensor_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_coordinates FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE speed > 50;
SELECT sensor_id, speed FROM vehicle_sensor_data ORDER BY sensor_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE speed BETWEEN 30 AND 60;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed FROM vehicle_sensor_data ORDER BY speed ASC, vehicle_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE speed > 100 ORDER BY vehicle_id DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_coordinates FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE sensor_id IN (1, 3, 5) ORDER BY sensor_id;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed, gps_coordinates FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE speed BETWEEN 50 AND 70 ORDER BY vehicle_id, speed DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE vehicle_id = 3 AND gps_coordinates LIKE '%North%' ORDER BY sensor_id;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_coordinates FROM vehicle_sensor_data WHERE speed < 50 OR speed > 80 ORDER BY vehicle_id, speed ASC;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_latitude, gps_longitude, speed FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE vehicle_id = 1;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed, gps_latitude, gps_longitude FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE vehicle_id = 2;
SELECT speed, gps_latitude, gps_longitude FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE vehicle_id = 3;
SELECT * FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE vehicle_id = 4;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_latitude, gps_longitude FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE speed > 60;
SELECT * FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE vehicle_id = 1;
SELECT gps_latitude, gps_longitude FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE speed > 80 ORDER BY vehicle_id DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, MAX(speed) AS max_speed FROM VehicleSensorData GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING max_speed > 100;
SELECT v.vehicle_id, vh.event_timestamp, vh.event_description FROM VehicleSensorData v JOIN VehicleHistory vh ON v.vehicle_id = vh.vehicle_id;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_latitude, gps_longitude, speed FROM VehicleSensorData WHERE speed < 50 ORDER BY gps_latitude ASC, gps_longitude DESC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_gps_data;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_coordinates, speed FROM vehicle_gps_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed FROM vehicle_speed_data WHERE speed > 50;
SELECT vehicle_id, route_id, average_speed FROM vehicle_analytics WHERE total_distance > 100 ORDER BY route_id ASC;
SELECT MAX(speed) AS max_speed, MIN(speed) AS min_speed, AVG(speed) AS avg_speed FROM vehicle_speed_data;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_gps_data WHERE vehicle_id = 1 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT route_id, average_speed FROM vehicle_analytics WHERE average_speed > 50 ORDER BY average_speed DESC;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed, timestamp FROM vehicle_speed_data WHERE speed BETWEEN 60 AND 80 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_coordinates FROM vehicle_gps_data WHERE gps_coordinates LIKE '%37.7749,-122.4194%' LIMIT 5;
SELECT vehicle_id, AVG(speed) AS avg_speed FROM vehicle_gps_data GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING avg_speed > 70 ORDER BY avg_speed DESC;
SELECT * FROM VehicleData;
SELECT vehicle_id, speed FROM VehicleData ORDER BY speed DESC;
SELECT * FROM VehicleEvents WHERE event_type = 'Engine Failure';
SELECT vehicle_id, total_distance FROM VehicleStatistics WHERE total_distance > 1000;
SELECT vehicle_id, error_message FROM VehicleErrors ORDER BY error_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM VehicleData ORDER BY vehicle_id DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT vehicle_id, gps_coordinates, speed FROM VehicleData WHERE speed > 50 ORDER BY gps_coordinates ASC;
SELECT vehicle_id, COUNT(event_id) AS total_events FROM VehicleEvents GROUP BY vehicle_id HAVING total_events >= 10;
SELECT v.vehicle_id, v.gps_coordinates, s.total_distance FROM VehicleData v JOIN VehicleStatistics s ON v.vehicle_id = s.vehicle_id WHERE s.total_distance > 10000 ORDER BY s.total_distance DESC;
SELECT e.error_id, e.vehicle_id, e.error_message, v.gps_coordinates FROM VehicleErrors e JOIN VehicleData v ON e.vehicle_id = v.vehicle_id WHERE v.speed = 0 ORDER BY e.error_timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_data LIMIT 10;
SELECT vehicle_id, latitude, longitude FROM vehicle_data WHERE speed > 50;
SELECT vehicle_id, timestamp FROM vehicle_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM vehicle_info WHERE manufacturer = 'Toyota';
SELECT vehicle_id, status, last_updated FROM vehicle_status WHERE status = 'active';
SELECT * FROM vehicle_data WHERE speed > 50 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT vehicle_id, latitude, longitude FROM vehicle_data WHERE latitude BETWEEN 40.0 AND 45.0 AND longitude BETWEEN -75.0 AND -70.0;
SELECT vehicle_id, status, last_updated FROM vehicle_status WHERE status = 'active' ORDER BY last_updated ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT vehicle_info.manufacturer, vehicle_info.model, vehicle_data.speed FROM vehicle_info JOIN vehicle_data ON vehicle_info.vehicle_id = vehicle_data.vehicle_id WHERE vehicle_data.speed < 40;
SELECT trip_id, start_timestamp, end_timestamp, start_latitude, start_longitude, end_latitude, end_longitude FROM trip_data WHERE end_timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY end_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
